# React Native GitHub Actions

## Orchestrators

| Workflow | Role |
|----------|------|
| `rn.yml` | Main CI: `detect` → JS lint/security/test → **bare:** `android-dev` / `ios-dev` (PR: artifacts; push: Firebase). **Expo:** EAS Android+iOS on PR when label **`run-eas`** (artifacts); **`eas-merge-gate`**; push: EAS + Firebase. `pull_request` types include `labeled` / `unlabeled`. Other: `rn-internal-release.yml`, `rn-firebase-release.yml` |
| `rn-internal-release.yml` | Manual: bare (Gradle + Fastlane) or `eas submit` (Expo) per platform |
| `rn-firebase-release.yml` | Manual Firebase App Distribution (bare only): `platform` = `android-dist` (prod APK), `android-dev`, `android-both`, `ios-dev`, `ios-dist`, `ios-both`, or `all` |
| `rn-code-health.yml` | Tech-debt / health scripts |
| `codeql-rn.yml` | CodeQL JavaScript |

## Reusable jobs (prefix `rn-job-`)

- **JS:** `rn-job-js-lint.yml`, `rn-job-js-test.yml`, `rn-job-security.yml`
- **Android:** `rn-job-android-build-bare.yml`, `rn-job-android-build-expo.yml`, `rn-job-android-internal-release-bare.yml`, `rn-job-android-internal-release-expo.yml`, `rn-job-android-debug-apk.yml`, `rn-job-android-firebase-release-bare.yml` (inputs `firebase_android_app` `dev`|`dist`, Gradle task + APK glob for flavor)
- **iOS:** `rn-job-ios-build-bare.yml`, `rn-job-ios-build-expo-local.yml`, `rn-job-ios-build-expo-cloud.yml`, `rn-job-ios-internal-release-bare.yml`, `rn-job-ios-internal-release-expo.yml`, `rn-job-ios-firebase-release-bare.yml` — plus **optional** (not called from default `rn.yml`): `rn-job-ios-simulator-artifact.yml`, `rn-job-ios-test.yml`
- **Expo (EAS in `rn.yml`):** `rn-job-expo-eas-build-and-distribute.yml` — cloud build (wait), download, workflow artifact, optional Firebase

## Path rules

- Run Gradle with `working-directory: android` or `cd android`; cache key `android/**/*.gradle*`.
- Write `android/local.properties` with `sdk.dir=$ANDROID_HOME` after `setup-android`.
- iOS: `bundle exec pod install --project-directory=ios`; use **workspace** `ios/TemplatePipelineReactNative.xcworkspace` (replace names in forks).
- Node **20** everywhere for JS and pre-Gradle steps.

## Workflow dispatch

`rn.yml` accepts `build_system` (`auto` \| `bare`; `auto` maps to `expo-local` when `eas.json` exists). Expo PR EAS runs only with label **`run-eas`**; configure **Rulesets** to require **`eas-merge-gate`** when you want merge blocking. `package_manager` is reserved for future pass-through to install scripts.

## Reuse in another repository

See **`docs/RN_WORKFLOW_REUSE.md`** — `rsync` kit, `bootstrap_rn_workflow_ids.py`, `list_workflow_secrets.py`, and the one-shot prompt **`CURSOR_RN_DEVOPS_ONE_SHOT_APPLY.txt`**.
